A vibrant, slightly psychedelic painting of a grizzled, leather-clad man in a Pulp Fiction-esque style, holding a syringe filled with a glowing, swirling liquid, with a muscular, monstrous creature dramatically enlarged and covered in +1/+1 counters, contrasted with rapidly diminishing -1/-1 counters, reflecting the card's mechanics, inspired by Quentin Tarantino's aesthetic.